---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Kunal" description="Privacy policy for findkunal.com.">
  <h1>Privacy</h1>
  <p>
    This site does not set tracking cookies and does not sell or share any
    personal data. Aggregate, anonymized analytics may be collected via
    Vercel Analytics to understand which pages are useful.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you contact me by email, I'll keep your message only as long as
    needed to respond. That's it.
  </p>
  <h2>Cookies & analytics</h2>
  <p>
    On your first visit you'll see a banner asking whether to allow
    privacy-friendly analytics. If you accept, an aggregate, anonymous
    analytics script is loaded (Vercel Analytics). If you reject — or
    ignore the banner — no analytics script is loaded. Your choice is
    stored locally in your browser. You can change it at any time by
    clearing your site data and reloading.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
